{"tid":760831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【配音員悲歌(3)】無綫滅台推出兩方案 原音上字幕 新聞部要做埋配音","createTime":"2018-07-30T01:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T13:59:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab7b213a6f3eaf03a579dbac6f2fa1a193e6546","tid":760831,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:41:15.000Z","msg":"9小時前21.7K<br />\n即時娛樂<br />\n <br />\n一名行內人士透露，無綫將會滅台及減少外購節目<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫於2015年時申請續牌時，確定至少每年提供12000小時嘅節目。<br />\n<br />\n無綫配音組「被裁員」，有傳未來仍會陸續有來，據行內人士透露，無綫將會滅台及減少外購節目，故此配音組嘅時數，將會由高峯期5,000個小時，會跌到3,500個小時。<br />\n<br />\n早前已傳出會滅台，主要取消收費電視嘅日劇、韓劇及華語劇台，到時配音組少咗三個重要據點。據該行內人士指，未來會以翡翠台、J2台、明珠台有需要嘅外購劇集或節目才配音，其他台則採用原音配字幕。<br />\n<br />\n至於過往財經資訊台外購嘅節目或紀錄片，配音組將不會再幫手配音，會改由新聞部自己負責，即係搵記者配埋。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，配音組嘅存亡，在於免費台製作嘅節目，粵語廣播嘅時數夠唔夠籌。鑑於無綫曾依賴外購內容嘅情況，故2015年續牌時，無綫承諾每年提供嘅服務，至少有12,000小時嘅節目為本地製作。行內人向本報稱，為咗滿足廣播條例，如果本地製作嘅時數唔夠，外購劇同節目配咗粵語後，都可以用嚟填時數，換言之配音組仲有存在價值。"},{"pid":"404845708b7b60964148d09608f9039133c7fcd6","tid":760831,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180730/58501047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F58501047&d=bAgHhObGkLxSANTR6DeyJy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=56a3740e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F58501047&h=67cbb626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180730/58501047</a>"},{"pid":"fbab03ee9b2fc296109d4761a855ae85bf02aa89","tid":760831,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"依家記者難撈 配音都要做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cec5e3f2bd01f0244c3155cf1fc2bb36c23b28","tid":760831,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:46:13.000Z","msg":"都唔好怪哂TVB, 成日都話有點樣o既觀眾就有點樣的電視台<br />\n望下連登入面其中一個comment<br />\n「話實話 d配音聲 真係好難頂 聽返原聲舒服好多」<br />\n我唔介意人地鍾意原聲, 但係都唔好講到班配音員無價值 lor<br />\n連呢一份專業都唔識尊重, 都唔怪得成個TVB D製作越黎越差都無人理"},{"pid":"47d105517002dbfa74d4f23bcc640ceb8ccdeaaf","tid":760831,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbab03ee9b2fc296109d4761a855ae85bf02aa89","tid":760831,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"依家記者難撈 配音都要做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"真係慘，又要開OT"},{"pid":"77011b16a2a1243ce02da6fe5196ff7938da2c07","tid":760831,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:15:23.000Z","msg":"香港班觀眾一向都鍾意聽原汁原味架啦<br />\n呢個時候又想屌tvb?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676e40a79e807f83be6d59f60003c35e7e2f3c5e","tid":760831,"uid":17504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"配音係比啲視力無咁好睇唔切啲字既觀眾可以欣賞吓外國劇啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d80286c3a746f93e892a3c8cebe2fbab257de6","tid":760831,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47d105517002dbfa74d4f23bcc640ceb8ccdeaaf","tid":760831,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbab03ee9b2fc296109d4761a855ae85bf02aa89","tid":760831,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"依家記者難撈 配音都要做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"真係慘，又要開OT"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"平時讀下稿，做政府喉舌<br />\n唔算好辛苦"}]}